Server Setup:

there is a running mail server on the server and there is a cron job that rus three times each 
hour . to access the server configration follow the belwo steps .

open internet browser 
go to : localhost:10000 and login
to access the mail sever select from the menu "server" and then select "Postfix Mail Server "
the mail server is only forwarding the emails using hotmail account.

to change the account details click on "SMTP Authentication And Encryption"

To modify the cron job select "system" from the upper menu then select "Scheduled Cron Jobs "
click on the cron job to modify it and then save it 

